definitions.definition: A village and civil parish in Buckinghamshire , England , previously in Aylesbury Vale district ( OS grid ref SP8118 ) .
Ellipsis of Weedon Bec : a village and civil parish in West Northamptonshire district, Northamptonshire , England , formerly in Daventry district ( OS grid ref SP6259 ) .
A municipality in Le Haut-Saint-François Regional County Municipality, Quebec , Canada .
A habitational surname from Old English .
